s: March 10, 2025 - Ascend mode is the main game mode in Amazon Ascension. The only way to play as tier 7 and tier 8 animals is to progress to them in ascend mode. All animals in tier 6 and below, as well as certain tier 7 animals (capybara and tucuxi if it gets added) can be played in free play.

March 10, 2025 - Animals are the "characters" you play as in Amazon ascension. All animals, including skins of animals, live in the Amazon or its surrounding areas. They can play in free play or ascend mode, assigned a tier based on their weight class. All animals have traits unique to their species.
